    <date day="21" month="February" year="2003"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies the enum: URI scheme. This URI is intended for
use where a resource address can be returned by evaluating the URI value
using the ENUM DDDS application. Syntactically, it uses a subset of the
format defined for the tel: URI scheme.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
